    "target": "_blank",
    "rel": "noreferrer"
  }), "hard enough"), " without it morphing\nand shapeshifting while we are trying to do it, so these days our industry mostly abandoned the idea of messing with code while it\u2019s running (except for some\n", mdx("a", _extends({
