    "id": "random-access-bag-of-records"
  }, "Random access bag of records"), mdx("p", null, "Sometimes reading all records one by one is not desirable and we need to be able to access any record as efficiently as possible. Ever noticed that in some compressed\nfiles you can quickly unpack any file inside it no matter how big the entire archive is and in some \u2014 you ", mdx("a", _extends({
    parentName: "p"
